				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just a little Erudite Trivia<BR>
<BR>
Their named after Erud, a former human that was mad at his own kind, so he sailed west from Qeynos and made a new town.<BR>
<BR>
They wear that shroud over their head becuase to Erudites, their brain is their mmost valuable weapon, so they protect it under the shroud. They look cool though...
				</font>
