				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Actually, Halas is even better.  You can level to level 5 almost instantaneously with the huge number of gnolls, ice goblins, polar bears, and especially wholly spiders. They are also worth a lot too.  <BR>
<BR>
From 5th to 15th level, the Tundra is an excellent hunting ground.  Just steadily go deeper as you increase in level.  I've got to level 12 in only a couple of days.  Great hunting area.
