	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Erudites make interesting paladins. They're a little on the frail side, but the high intelligence definitely makes learning new skills a lot easier. I gained 20 swimming skill points in about an hour, and learned to speak troll in about half an hour (my troll is &quot;Excellent&quot;). And Erudite paladins also learn combat skills quite quickly. There's a handoff, but it's not too bad (and as someone else noted, we look snazzy all decked out in our gear!).
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
